---
title: Home
description: Collected writings on DeFi, data, MEV, and math by Evan Kim.
layout: base.njk
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <span class="eyebrow">Evan Kim</span>
    <h1>Collected Writings</h1>
    <p class="hero-tagline">
      Research, builds, and notes on DeFi, data infrastructure, MEV, and math.
    </p>
    <p class="hero-links">
      <a href="https://github.com/Evan-Kim2028" class="pill">GitHub</a>
      <a href="https://x.com/EvanDeKim" class="pill">Twitter</a>
      <a href="https://dune.com/evandekim" class="pill">Dune</a>
      <a href="https://app.sentio.xyz/evandekim/sui-lst/dashboards/6fO9DNrQ" class="pill">Sentio</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="featured">
  <div class="section-header">
    <h2>Featured Writings</h2>
    <a href="{{ '/writings/' | url }}" class="all-link">View all →</a>
  </div>
  <div class="featured-grid">
  {% for writing in collections.writings | sortByDate | limit(6) %}
    <article class="featured-card">
      <a href="{{ writing.url | url }}" class="card-title">{{ writing.data.title }}</a>
      <p class="card-excerpt">{{ writing.templateContent | excerpt }}</p>
      <div class="card-meta">
        <span class="card-collection">{{ writing.data.collection }}</span>
        <span>{{ writing.data.date | formatDate }}</span>
      </div>
    </article>
  {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<section class="collections-overview">
  <div class="section-header">
    <h2>Browse by Collection</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="collection-grid">
    <a href="{{ '/collections/latest/' | url }}" class="card">
      <span class="card-name">Latest</span>
      <span class="card-count">{{ collections.writings | countByCollection('latest') }} writings</span>
    </a>
    <a href="{{ '/collections/highlights/' | url }}" class="card">
      <span class="card-name">Highlights</span>
      <span class="card-count">{{ collections.writings | countByCollection('highlights') }} writings</span>
    </a>
    <a href="{{ '/collections/data/' | url }}" class="card">
      <span class="card-name">Data</span>
      <span class="card-count">{{ collections.writings | countByCollection('data') }} writings</span>
    </a>
    <a href="{{ '/collections/mev/' | url }}" class="card">
      <span class="card-name">MEV</span>
      <span class="card-count">{{ collections.writings | countByCollection('mev') }} writings</span>
    </a>
    <a href="{{ '/collections/defi/' | url }}" class="card">
      <span class="card-name">DeFi</span>
      <span class="card-count">{{ collections.writings | countByCollection('defi') }} writings</span>
    </a>
    <a href="{{ '/collections/math/' | url }}" class="card">
      <span class="card-name">Math</span>
      <span class="card-count">{{ collections.writings | countByCollection('math') }} writings</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="about">
  <h2>About</h2>
  <p>
    I'm a researcher and builder working at the intersection of blockchain data, DeFi mechanisms, and applied math.
    This archive collects my past work across Paragraph, Mirror, ethresear.ch, and GitHub —
    reorganized so it's easier to browse, reference, and search.
  </p>
  <p>
    All content is also exposed through a local MCP server so you can query it directly from Claude.
    See the <a href="{{ '/llms-full.txt' | url }}">full-text index</a> or the <a href="https://github.com/Evan-Kim2028/evan_writings">source repo</a>.
  </p>
</section>
